        "description": {
            "value": "<p>One of your forebears hailed from a celestial realm, or your ancestors' devotion led to their lineage being blessed.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> divine</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Diplomacy, Religion</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Light]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Heal]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spiritual Weapon]</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Holy Light]{Searing Light}</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Wrath]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Flame Strike]</em>, 6th:<em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Blade Barrier]</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Decree]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Aura]</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Foresight]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Angelic Halo]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Angelic Wings]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Celestial Brand]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> An angelic aura protects you or one target, granting a +1 status bonus to saving throws for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Angelic Blood Magic]</p>"
